<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Bastinado" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Bastinado,</orth> a sound beating: <cit><quote>I will deal in poison with thee, or in b., or in steel,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.1.60" default="NO" valid="yes">As V, 1, 60</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>he gives the b. with his tongue,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 2.463" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 463</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>gave Amamon the b.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.370" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 370</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>